'''加拿大工業部'''（{{lang-en|'''Industry Canada'''}}、{{lang-fr|'''Industrie Canada'''}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]]政府部門之一，負責區域經濟發展、投資與創新/[[研發|研發]]。工業部在全國各地共有6,104名全職職員。<ref name="about">{{cite web|url=http://www.ic.gc.ca/cmb/welcomeic.nsf/ICPages/Department|title=The Department - Industry Canada|accessdate=2006-08-30|archive-date=2006-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831030014/http://www.ic.gc.ca/cmb/welcomeic.nsf/ICPages/Department|dead-url=no}}</ref>
